- Run the app: python app.py


- Open in browser:
http://127.0.0.1:5000/



üìñ Learning Highlights
- Implemented linear search for filtering flights
- Used Timsort via Python‚Äôs list.sort() for sorting
- Practiced session management to persist search results
- Enhanced UI/UX with opacity, color styling, and responsive design

